```
// Base url will be updated once provided.

 ```

## Headers

`Accept: application/json`

`Content-Type: application/json`

For requests containing media files:

`Content-Type: multipart/form-data`

## Authentication

Authentication is provided using cookie based session authentication. This ensures CSRF protection, session authentication and protects against leakage of the authentication credentials via XSS.

**NOTE:** _The token used in this collection is only for use in the postman collection and does not return a token._

To Authenticate, call the `\register` (for new users) or `\login` (for returning users) after initializing CSRF protection like so:

``` javascript
axios.get('/sanctum/csrf-cookie').then(response => {
    // Call Registeration with user details
                 // OR
    // Call Login with user credentials...
});

 ```

